# ── repo-root whitelist ──
# Ad-hoc test binaries (t1, verify_foo, repro, …) constantly land in the
# repo root during development; there were ~400 of them. Ignore everything
# at top level except the known project files and directories — a new
# tracked root entry needs a !/name line here.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/CLAUDE.md
!/CLAUDE_DEEP_DIVE.md
!/FEATURES.md
!/LICENSE
!/Makefile
!/README.md
!/configure
!/strada
!/benchmarks/
!/bootstrap/
!/compiler/
!/docs/
!/examples/
!/interpreter/
!/lib/
!/perl/
!/runtime/
!/t/
!/tools/
!/vendor/

# Compiled benchmark binaries (extensionless siblings of bench_*.strada)
benchmarks/bench_*
!benchmarks/bench_*.*
